OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781308974
OL,3,CFour Palestine Action activists jailed
OL,4,Cover #1.2m factory raid
OL,6,FFour Palestine Action activists who
OL,7,Fmounted a raid on an Israel-based
OL,8,Fdefence firm's UK factory, causing
OL,9,F#1.2 million of damage and leaving a
OL,10,Fpolice officer with a fractured spine,
OL,11,Fhave been jailed.
OL,13,FCharlotte Head, 30, Samuel Corner, 23,
OL,14,FLeona Kamio, 30, and Fatema Rajwani,
OL,15,F21, used an old prison van to crash
OL,16,Finto the Elbit Systems site near
OL,17,FBristol in the early hours of August 6
OL,18,F2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781308974
OL,3,CFour Palestine Action activists jailed
OL,4,Cover #1.2m factory raid
OL,6,FThe activists used sledgehammers and
OL,7,Fcrowbars to destroy computers, drones
OL,8,Fand other equipment before police and
OL,9,Fsecurity intervened.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FCorner, a former student at Oxford,
OL,17,Fwas jailed for seven years and eight
OL,18,Fmonths after striking police officer
OL,19,FKate Evans twice on the back with a
OL,20,Fseven-pound sledgehammer, leaving her
OL,21,Fwith a fractured spine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781308974
OL,3,CFour Palestine Action activists jailed
OL,4,Cover #1.2m factory raid
OL,6,FJudge Jeremy Johnson told Corner he
OL,7,Fhad used "extreme and gratuitous force
OL,8,Fagainst a vulnerable police officer
OL,9,Facting in the course of her duties".
OL,11,FHead, who drove the prison van into
OL,12,Fthe compound, and Kamio were both
OL,13,Fsentenced to five years in prison, and
OL,14,FRajwani received a sentence of four
OL,15,Fyears and eight months.
OL,17,FEach defendant will also spend an
OL,18,Fextra year on licence once their
OL,19,Fprison terms have ended.
OL,26,@oD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781308974
OL,3,CFour Palestine Action activists jailed
OL,4,Cover #1.2m factory raid
OL,6,FSupporters of the defendants cheered
OL,7,Fand banged on the front of the public
OL,8,Fgallery as the sentences were passed.
OL,10,FThe judge said the group had "decided
OL,11,Fto take matters into your own hands"
OL,12,Fover Israel's war in Gaza, and were
OL,13,F"disillusioned" with legal efforts to
OL,14,Foppose it.
OL,16,FHe said the activists had been
OL,17,F"reckless" about who would be injured,
OL,18,Fand had been heavily involved in
OL,19,Forganising the raid with the right of
OL,20,Fveto over each part of the plan.
OL,26,@rD@^OUsD@dO]uD@AOUyD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781308974
OL,3,CFour Palestine Action activists jailed
OL,4,Cover #1.2m factory raid
OL,6,FTwo of the activists had livestreamed
OL,7,Fthe raid and posted the footage to
OL,8,Fsocial media as part of an effort to
OL,9,F"glorify criminality and vigilantism",
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,FThe judge ruled that the raid amounted
OL,13,Fto an "act of terrorism", having been
OL,14,Fcarried out to try to influence the UK
OL,15,Fgovernment's position on Gaza and
OL,16,Fintimidate a section of the public.
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@GOUuD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
