OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781308974
OL,3,CFour Palestine Action activists jailed
OL,4,Cover #1.2m factory raid
OL,6,FEarlier on Friday, officer Evans
OL,7,Frevealed she had been forced to give
OL,8,Fup her rank of sergeant after
OL,9,Fstruggling following Corner's attack
OL,10,Fand said she is still having medical
OL,11,Ftreatment nearly two years later.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781308974
OL,3,CFour Palestine Action activists jailed
OL,4,Cover #1.2m factory raid
OL,6,FRajiv Menon KC, representing Head, had
OL,7,Fargued that the judge should not take
OL,8,Fthe unprecedented step of finding a
OL,9,F"terrorist connection" for offences of
OL,10,Fcriminal damage, but the prosecutor
OL,11,Fsaid the scale of the damage, combined
OL,12,Fwith Palestine Action's aim to
OL,13,F"influence government decisions and
OL,14,Fpolicies" in the UK and Israel, meant
OL,15,Fit qualified.
OL,17,FThe four activists will serve at least
OL,18,Ftwo-thirds of their sentences, and
OL,19,Fwill have to face Parole Board
OL,20,Fhearings to secure their release from
OL,21,Fprison.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@VO]uD@AOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
