OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781308974
OL,3,CFour Palestine Action activists jailed
OL,4,Cover #1.2m factory raid
OL,6,FThey are also expected to be subjected
OL,7,Fto extra monitoring once out of jail,
OL,8,Fand will spend an extra year on
OL,9,Flicence after the end of their prison
OL,10,Fterms, as well as 15 years being
OL,11,Fsubject to terrorist notification
OL,12,Frequirements.
OL,14,FAround 500 protesters gathered outside
OL,15,Fthe court on Friday for a
OL,16,Fdemonstration in support of the
OL,17,Fdefendants in the dock.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781308974
OL,3,CFour Palestine Action activists jailed
OL,4,Cover #1.2m factory raid
OL,6,FAmid a heavy police presence, at least
OL,7,F72 of those at the demonstration were
OL,8,Farrested after being seen holding up
OL,9,Fsigns in support of the now-proscribed
OL,10,Fterrorist organisation Palestine
OL,11,FAction.
OL,13,FElbit Systems was founded in 1966 and
OL,14,Fis an international military
OL,15,Ftechnology company supplying equipment
OL,16,Fand drones to the Israeli military.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
