FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781308974
OL,3,CFour Palestine Action activists jailed
OL,4,Cover #1.2m factory raid
OL,6,FThe firm received a #1.2 million
OL,7,Finsurance payout after the Palestine
OL,8,FAction raid, and Elbit security
OL,9,Fmanager Simon Robinson said more
OL,10,Fserious harm had been done to staff
OL,11,Fleft fearful of future attacks.
OL,13,FThe Palestine Action activists say
OL,14,Fthey carried out the raid to destroy
OL,15,Fequipment that would have been used
OL,16,Fagainst Palestinians in Gaza, and say
OL,17,Ftheir actions were necessary to oppose
OL,18,Fgenocide.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
